Every font you use adds to the page's load time.

A font face is a single permutation of weight, slope, etc? (p49)

For each face such as bolder weight or an italic type the same rule must be duplicated with extra descriptors added to the new rule.

When using web fonts you must define a link to the appropriate file for each different font face you use.

